reviews.review_text:
Carlos also on Watchtower. Thanx Danny, Adam & Derek.  I lost my 1st set and set II is a nice upgrade.  I sat near the tape's origin.
Everything is very solid.  Nice show beginning to end.  Carlos really lights up Aiko!  During the Watchtower Carlos & Jerry trade solos, each one getting more fiery.  I remember After Jerry's last blistering lead he nodded to Carlos to go again.  He gave Jerry a respectful bow and shook him off.  What a great moment.  Peace.
